snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Text Messages, Michael Jace Conviction vesves Blake Leibel’s Insanity Plea
snippet.description:
Johnny Depps estranged wife, Amber Heard, has now released text messages between herself and Depps assistant to prove Depp engaged in a pattern of physical abuse against her. We discuss.





The case of Blake Leibel, a 35-year-old Canadian man who was charged this week with torturing, mutilating and killing his girlfriend in their Hollywood apartment, is explored with k Ebner.
